## Skills and reusable guidance

Repo-local skills live in:
- `skills/` (portable across tools)

Tool-specific helper skills (may be installed per-tool, but can be read in-repo when present):
- `.claude/skills/` (Claude-only helpers; do not put general workflow docs here)
- `.agents/skills/` (maintainer/internal workflows when present)

When you need a skill, prefer:
- first: repo-local `skills/`
- then: tool-provided skills (if available in the runtime)

